ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[The original paper by Cottone et al. referred to in this report can be read
in the American Journal of Gastroenterology 2001 Mar;96(3):773-5. Prevalence
of cytomegalovirus infection in severe refractory ulcerative and Crohn's
colitis. - Mod.CP]
